{"tid":124014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［發夢撚］分享下你發過最特別既夢","createTime":"2017-02-17T09:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T06:22:55.000Z","uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0233dcffa822f72e0d94271ae8efefa7d38dcef1","tid":124014,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"忽然好奇大家發過咩有趣既夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學雞果陣迷過一排哈利波特<br />\n有次發夢我比人追殺<br />\n個背景係夜晚落雨行哂雷咁<br />\n我騎住飛天掃帚係屋頂飛<br />\n係D高樓大廈左穿右插<br />\n結果係屋頂比人圍死左<br />\n重點係有離心力 好真實<br />\n醒果陣對手臂勁攰 <br />\n因為捉掃帚捉得太實<br />\n驚個人會跌落街<br />\n但係我覺得勁好玩勁正<br />\n爽過玩機動遊戲<br />\n<br />\n之後我好開心同fd分享呢個夢<br />\n點知我啲fd淨係問左我<br />\n........<br />\n......<br />\n.....<br />\n...<br />\n..<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你條撚仲有冇感覺</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f306f7f3cae83b2a48867191d199bb2a91a361","tid":124014,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"同個女仔扑野<br />\n射個陣就醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c954b62c0e0b2476eb3ad09007bd53cda0e22b","tid":124014,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"平時我老公會趁我唔為意用鬍鬚拮我塊臉<br />\n有一排成日偷襲我 <br />\n結果有一晚我發夢佢㩒住我係梳化又係咁拮我<br />\n然後我發脾氣好嬲谷到爆生出左鬚根<br />\n再一個反身將佢壓返落床狂拮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我醒返講比老公聽<br />\n佢反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi